Active Cover System. Rack up solo or co-op high scores as Red-Eye or Magnum - two undercover agents too cool to stay undercover - in the action-packed buddy-cop campaign.\n\nYour mission: infiltrate evil megacorp Infinidyne, take down CEO Pax Harrison, and shut down his mind-control technology before he turns billions into cybernetic meat puppets.\n\n\u2022 Classic lightgun arcade action, made for VR.\n\u2022 Take on Infinidyne solo with an AI partner or co-op with an online friend.\n\u2022 Reload and dodge enemy fire like an action hero with the Active Cover System.\n\u2022 Over-the-top cinematic action with explosions, bullet time, and environmental destruction.\n\u2022 Retro score system rewards aim, speed, and chained kills.\n\u2022 Use your skills, the environment, and a wide variety of special weapons to take out goons, advanced enemies, and Infinidyne bosses.\n\nAre you ready to go Under Cover?", "short_description": "Under Cover: a Lightgun Cover Shooter inspired by arcade classics.\n\nDuck to reload with the groundbreaking Active Cover System. Rack up solo or co-op high scores as Red-Eye or Magnum - two undercover agents too cool to stay undercover - in the action-packed buddy-cop campaign."}]}, "developer_name": "Sigtrap", "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://coatsink.com/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "Coatsink", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://coatsink.com/games/undercover", "category": null, "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "1592192974313489"}, {"id": "1436351953220286"}, {"id": "459781504968480"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": [], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "NOT_REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app